   - Add an event listener to the `open-modal` button to open the modal.
   - Add an event listener to the `close` button to close the modal.

### Final Code

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Chatbot with Modal</title>
    <style>
      /* Chatbot Container */
      .chatbot-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      /* Modal */
